N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. tit. 6, ch. I, subch. E, pt. 37 - Sale Of Certain Lake Ontario Fishes Prohibited

State Regulations
§ 37.1 - Regulation prohibiting the sale of certain fishes taken from Lake Ontario, its tributaries and the St. Lawrence River

Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. tit. 6, ch. I, subch. E, pt. 37

Statutory authority: Environmental Conservation Law, §§11-0317 and 11-0325

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
